title: HOUR 2 - Joy Taylor Shares Her Favorite 5 in the NFL!
itunes:title: HOUR 2 - Joy Taylor Shares Her Favorite 5 in the NFL!
description:
In this hour of The Herd with Colin Cowherd, Joy Taylor--in for Colin--shares her "Favorite 5" upcoming NFL games. Plus, FS1 NBA analyst Ric Bucher joins Joy to discuss the league's Christmas Day games and the Covid issues plaguing rosters. Also, Joy mulls over some of the MVP, DPOY, and COY candidates in the NFL. Finally, FS1 NFL analyst Greg Jennings chats with Joy about some of the NFL's pertinent storylines.
